    <item>
      <title>About Dr. Vishal Kotha</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/vishal-profile.jpg&#34; class=&#34;profile-circle&#34; alt=&#34;Dr. Vishal Kotha&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am a &lt;strong&gt;Materials Scientist&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Data Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; dedicated to bridging the gap between atomic-level design and real-world energy applications. With a Ph.D. from &lt;strong&gt;IIT Bombay&lt;/strong&gt; and postdoctoral experience at the &lt;strong&gt;Weizmann Institute of Science&lt;/strong&gt;, I specialize in synthesizing transition metal perovskite oxides for green hydrogen and next-gen batteries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;my-philosophy-conscious-science&#34;&gt;My Philosophy: &amp;ldquo;Conscious Science&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My approach to research is grounded in the belief that &lt;strong&gt;precision in the laboratory begins with precision of the mind.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
